#compdef de-macro
# Documentation: https://ctan.org/tex-archive/support/de-macro
# Reference accessed: 2026-05-17
# Verified: upstream docs at the URL above.

# de-macro: Peter Gacs's LaTeX private-macro eliminator. Per the
# upstream usage string `de-macro [--defs ...] [.tex] ...`,
# the only documented flag is --defs.

_arguments -s -S \
  '--defs[treat following file as a defs file]:defs file:_files -g "*.tex"' \
  '*:TeX file:_files -g "*.tex"'
